ought.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aCanadian essays. 0aLiterature. 0aPoetry. 4aLiterary Criticism. 4aLiterary Criticism: Canadian Literature. 4aPoetry. 7aPOETRY / Canadian.2bisacsh1 aBoone, Laurel, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package Pre-2010z978311127416408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package pre 2010z978311127724040uhttps://doi.org/10.51644/978088920877340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780889208773423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780889208773/original  a978-3-11-127416-4  ACUP Complete eBook-Package Pre-2010b2010  a978-3-11-127724-0  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package pre 2010b2010  aGBV-deGruyter-alles